    <item>
      <title>习近平称中国已准备好与特朗普合作提升两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/xi-says-china-is-ready-to-work-with-trump-to-boost-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国领导人习近平对美国总统乔·拜登表示，他已准备好与唐纳德·特朗普合作，改善世界两大经济体之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/xi-says-china-is-ready-to-work-with-trump-to-boost-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 21:16:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国通胀率出现波动或为英国央行谨慎情绪提供依据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/uk-inflation-hiccup-may-buttress-case-for-boe-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国10月份通胀率可能再次飙升至英国央行的目标水平之上，这进一步表明政策制定者在降息时应谨慎行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/uk-inflation-hiccup-may-buttress-case-for-boe-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对 SRT 信用风险的担忧日益加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/concerns-about-credit-risk-in-srts-are-growing-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在监管机构警告重大风险转移（一种银行资本减免）可能对金融稳定构成风险的背景下，市场参与者越来越担心此类转移带来的信用风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/concerns-about-credit-risk-in-srts-are-growing-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
